Update from Scott. Meeting went “very well"
Brand team is totally on board.

>Heads of Identity and Brand Design loved Chameleon and Compass and will begin to process how they can support what we are  doing.  They looked and were very supportive on all levels, convinced with the how both the App and Device is ‘Born from Culture, Built for Purpose and Daringly Simple’.  This is the new language we are using together in the  brand to refer to our design process btw, and how to frame discussions around design direction - so I structured the conversation around those questions.

>DESIGN:
>One last comment.  As it was stated yesterday, the look and feel has grown up and we have arrived at something which is working on multiple levels now, through color, type, texture, balance and intuition for the interaction models discussed.
Fantastic work everyone!
